#web-landing-one
  .jumbotron.text-center
    .container
      %h1#header Find Your Next Sales Superstar
      %p Discover more than 5,000 unique travel destinations around the world and <br> start planning your next adventure.
      = link_to "Get Started", new_employer_registration_path, class: "btn btn-default btn-lg"
    .responsive-note
      %span#responsive

  / .testimonial
  /   = link_to 'X', '#', class: "close-testimonial close-btn", id: "optional"

  .benefit1
    .container
      .text-center
        %h2 We curate to find the most experienced and highest calibre talent using technology and data analytics to cut traditional overhead and save you thousands of dollars. 

        %hr

      .row
        .col-md-7
          = image_tag "web-screen.png", class: "img-responsive"
        .col-md-5
          %h2 Increased Sales Productivity
          %p Research shows that placing the right salespeople in the right job allows them to become instantly more productive. Let SalesMatchr identify the applicants that will ramp up faster than others. This means less time on-boarding and more time spent doing what they were hired for: closing deals and growing your company’s bottom line.

  .benefit2
    .container
      .row
        .col-md-5
          %h2 Qualified applicants delivered directly to your inbox.
          %p One of the biggest problems in hiring sales talent is maintaining an active talent pool. Without anyone in queue, there is a rush to hire each and every time a position opens up. SalesMatchr consistently delivers high quality candidates that fit your needs.
        .col-md-7
          = image_tag "web-screen.png", class: "img-responsive"

  .benefit3
    .container
      .row
        .col-md-7
          = image_tag "web-screen.png", class: "img-responsive"
        .col-md-5
          %h2 Hire the right salespeople
          %p Sales recruiting is notoriously subjective, inefficient, and expensive. The typical process uses a shotgun approach that often results in unproductive hires. SalesMatchr develops an objective, data-driven success profile based on your existing top performers to find the best candidates to join your sales team. 

  .call-to-action.text-center
    .container
      %h1{:contenteditable => true} Ready for an adventure?
      %p{:contenteditable => true} Pie jujubes bonbon sugar plum dragée tart jelly cookie donut. Apple pie sweet roll caramels <br> sweet brownie. Apple pie powder biscuit gummies.
      = link_to "Get Started", new_employer_registration_path, class: "btn btn-default btn-lg"

  .pricing
    = link_to "X", '#', class: "close-pricing close-btn"
    .container.text-center
      .pricing-header
        %h2{:contenteditable => true} Plans and Pricing
        %p{:contenteditable => true} Travelist is free to use for public trips. Plan private trips with any of our paid plans.
      .row
        .col-md-4
          .price-container.regular-offer
            %h4{:contenteditable => true} Standard Plan
            .price
              %p{:contenteditable => true} $9
              %p.month{:contenteditable => true} /album
            = link_to 'Choose Plan', '#', class: "btn"
        .col-md-4
          .popular-header
            %h4{:contenteditable => true} Most Popular
          .popular-container
            %h4{:contenteditable => true} Startup Plan
            .price
              %p{:contenteditable => true} $29
              %p.month{:contenteditable => true} /album
            = link_to 'Choose Plan', '#', class: "btn"
        .col-md-4
          .price-container.regular-offer
            %h4{:contenteditable => true} Enterprise Plan
            .price
              %p{:contenteditable => true} $59
              %p.month{:contenteditable => true} /album
            = link_to 'Choose Plan', '#', class: "btn"

